snippet.title: Commodore C64 - Dandy (1986)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Dandy is the massive arcade adventure that takes you through some of the most detailed dungeons you've ever seen. Either solo or with a (brave) friend you can hack, thump and zap your way through spectres, necromancers and other dungeon-dwellers whose concern for your health and well-being is zero.
